英译中：(a) your face was not within view of the camera for all of the exam (see approximately 
00:01:50, 00:25:40, 00:37:58, 00:55:42 of the camera recording);
(b) you were observed picking something up, a sound could be heard and a reflection of a 
second device could be seen in your glasses (see approximately 00:00:09 of the 
camera recording). Following this, a flash of light could be seen in your glasses and a 
sound of you placing something down on the table could be heard (see approximately 
00:00:25 to 00:00:29 of the camera recording);
(c) sounds of you picking something up and placing something down on the table could be 
heard throughout the exam (see approximately 00:04:30, 00:19:37, 00:20:27,
00:24:01, 00:40:36, 00:54:43 of the camera recording);
